paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
select month, 
        sum(case when lower(utmSource) like '%criteo%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_d1_new%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_non_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%criteo_re-engagement_android_non buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%criteo_re-engagement_android_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_appd1plus_combined%') 
                  and (lower(utmMedium) like '%disp_rmkt%' or lower(utmMedium) like '%retargeting%') 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%app%' 
                 then nm end) as Criteo_App,
        sum(case when lower(utmSource) like '%criteo%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%web_lower_funnel_1d%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_nonbuyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_webd1plus_combined%') 
                  and lower(utmMedium) like '%disp_rmkt%' 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%web%' 
                 then nm end) as Criteo_Web,
        sum(case when lower(utmSource) like '%rtbhouse%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus_nonbuyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus_buyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1_buyers%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_appd1plus_combined%' ) 
                  and lower(utmMedium) like '%appretargeting%' 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%app%' 
                 then nm end) as Rtbhouse_App,
        sum(case when lower(utmSource) like '%rtbhouse%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus_nonbuyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus_buyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1_buyers%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_webd1plus_combined%' ) 
                  and (lower(utmContent) like '%webretargeting%' or lower(utmContent) like '%rtbcllanding%' or lower(utmContent) like '%_rtb_cl_landing_%')
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%web%' 
                 then nm end) as Rtbhouse_Web
from `temp.c` 
group by month
order by month
",1000)

paragraphs.title: Retargeting_6Months_NM_Orders
paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
select month, 
        sum(case when lower(utmSource) like '%criteo%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_d1_new%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_non_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%criteo_re-engagement_android_non buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%criteo_re-engagement_android_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_appd1plus_combined%') 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%app%' 
                 then nm end) as Criteo_App,
        sum(case when lower(utmSource) like '%criteo%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%web_lower_funnel_1d%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_nonbuyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_webd1plus_combined%') 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%web%' 
                 then nm end) as Criteo_Web,
        sum(case when lower(utmSource) like '%rtbhouse%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus_nonbuyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus_buyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1_buyers%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_appd1plus_combined%' ) 
                  and lower(utmContent) like '%appretargeting%' 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%app%' 
                 then nm end) as Rtbhouse_App,
        sum(case when lower(utmSource) like '%rtbhouse%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus_nonbuyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus_buyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1_buyers%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_webd1plus_combined%' ) 
                  and (lower(utmContent) like '%webretargeting%' or lower(utmContent) like '%rtbcllanding%')
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%web%' 
                 then nm end) as Rtbhouse_Web,
        count(distinct case when lower(utmSource) like '%criteo%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_d1_new%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_non_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%criteo_re-engagement_android_non buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_inapp_android_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%criteo_re-engagement_android_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_appd1plus_combined%') 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%app%' 
                 then subOrderId end) as Criteo_App_Orders,
        count(distinct case when lower(utmSource) like '%criteo%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%web_lower_funnel_1d%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_nonbuyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%snapdeal_web_buyers_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_webd1plus_combined%') 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%web%' 
                 then subOrderId end) as Criteo_Web_Orders,
        count(distinct case when lower(utmSource) like '%rtbhouse%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus_nonbuyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_app_d1plus_buyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1_buyers%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_appd1plus_combined%' ) 
                  and lower(utmContent) like '%appretargeting%' 
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%app%' 
                 then subOrderId end) as Rtbhouse_App_Orders,
        count(distinct case when lower(utmSource) like '%rtbhouse%' 
                  and (lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_d1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus_nonbuyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse_retargeting_web_d1plus_buyer%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%rtbhouse-retargeting_postd1_buyers%' or lower(utmCampaign) like '%sd_webd1plus_combined%' ) 
                  and (lower(utmContent) like '%webretargeting%' or lower(utmContent) like '%rtbcllanding%')
                  and lower(deviceType) like '%web%'
                 then subOrderId end) as Rtbhouse_Web_Orders
from `temp.c` 
group by month
order by month
",1000)

paragraphs.title: Affiliates_6Months_NM_Orders
paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
select distinct month, 
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%interest%'
                     then nm end) as Adinterest,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%admit%'
                     then nm end) as Admit,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%affinity%'
                     then nm end) as Affinity,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%affnet%'
                     then nm end) as Affnet,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%affyguru%'
                     then nm end) as Affyguru,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%cash%' or lower(utmContent) like '%earn%'
                     then nm end) as Cash,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%coupondunia%'
                     then nm end) as Coupondunia,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%cuelinks%' or lower(utmContent) like '%desidime%' 
                     then nm end) as Cuelinks,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%globale%'
                     then nm end) as Globale,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%gopaisa%'
                     then nm end) as Gopaisa,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%grabon%'
                     then nm end) as Grabon,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%icubes%'
                     then nm end) as Icubes,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%inr%'
                     then nm end) as Inr,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%xpedia%'
                     then nm end) as Mediaxpedia,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%avenue%'
                     then nm end) as Mobavenue,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%optimise%'
                     then nm end) as Optimise,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%wapas%'
                     then nm end) as Paisawapas,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%spiffy%'
                     then nm end) as Click2commission,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%leaf%'
                     then nm end) as Valueleaf,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%whiz%'
                     then nm end) as Whizadsbay,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%xap%'
                     then nm end) as Xapads,
                sum(case when lower(utmContent) like '%xare%'
                     then nm end) as Xare
                     
from(
select distinct a.orderDate,
                substr(a.orderDate,1,7) as month,
                a.utmSource,
                a.utmCampaign,
                a.utmContent,
                a.utmMedium,
                a.deviceType,
                a.pogId, 
                sum(b.NMIncAd) as nm 
from `temp.a` a 
left join `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)` b
on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
group by a.orderDate,a.pogId,a.utmSource, a.utmCampaign, a.utmContent, a.deviceType, a.utmMedium)
where month in ('2022-11','2022-12','2023-01','2023-02','2023-03','2023-04')
group by month
order by month
",1000)
